{"tid":2496968,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港青創業 視員工為親人  英國黃店賣港貨 柴米油鹽附文宣","createTime":"2021-04-20T07:38:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T07:38:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f77d28fe5067311010a93a96250a4175747280fb","tid":2496968,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T07:38:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210420/O7XIMNMIBBDRDBBROL2HVOYHFA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210420%2FO7XIMNMIBBDRDBBROL2HVOYHFA%2F&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuP7iMF%2BZ1QNuv%2BvReNsMrP0%3D&h=09813c0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210420%2FO7XIMNMIBBDRDBBROL2HVOYHFA%2F&h=73d5151b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210420/O7XIMNMIBBDRDBBROL2HVOYHFA/</a><br />\n<br />\n港青創業 視員工為親人 <br />\n英國黃店賣港貨 柴米油鹽附文宣<br />\n<br />\n【力撐手足】在英國，提到要購買中式食品及產品，首先想起的是四大連鎖華人超市。三年前，有港人在英創立網上亞洲食品超市「華南行」，除售賣亞洲食品，也盡力引入更多香港品牌。華南行曾隨貨附送抗爭文宣、引入黃圈產品、捐錢給612人道支援基金，有人形容是英國黃店，創辦人說來淡然︰「你覺得要做、應該做，就會去做㗎啦」。<br />\n<br />\n駐英記者︰李雨夢<br />\n<br />\n踏進華南行位於東倫敦的倉庫，數名員工正忙着執貨，負責人Magic在電腦前埋首工作。貨櫃上有來自港、日、韓、泰、台、中的產品，熱浪薯片、樂天熊仔餅、冠益華記辣椒醬等在港常見而英國罕見的產品。<br />\n<br />\nMagic於2018年創立華南行。談到創業緣起，得從大學畢業說起，當時才20出頭的他申請到英國工作假期，先後在印度及韓國的食品公司工作過，後來回港，又在太古可口可樂上班，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n兩年後工作簽證將過期，迫使Magic思考下一步，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nMagic一直爭取引入多些香港品牌及產品，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-aCjV4tPKOdxcVs2pjxL6bv7Ln8=/510x339/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O3TD72ZYSRFNJOMXUQKCOE5JFQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-aCjV4tPKOdxcVs2pjxL6bv7Ln8%3D%2F510x339%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FO3TD72ZYSRFNJOMXUQKCOE5JFQ.jpg&h=f1af43e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■華南行貨架擺滿來自亞洲的各類型食品，對於公司，對於自己，Magic強調初心沒變。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「好無助，最多只係不斷refresh個facebook、新聞，冇咩可以做到。」<br />\n<br />\n2019年，香港爆發反送中運動，身處英國的他只能隔岸觀看，「好無助，最多只係不斷refresh個facebook、新聞，冇咩可以做到」，後來看到Telegram群組有人問，有沒有人可以在英國幫忙派發文宣，「我哋可以喎，我話我呢邊有間公司，盡力囉，派到幾多得幾多」。<br />\n<br />\n那時開始，每接定單，Magic都隨貨附送文宣。「有。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n華南行早前引入設計平台Project R產品，包括印有「HONGKONGER」字眼衞衣及「自由之籽」帆布袋，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n從發放文宣到引入黃圈產品，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n華南行目前已聘請了五、六名員工，大部份是港人。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n獨自在外創業，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n「有啲後生仔嚟到好急趕，冇咩準備，就盡力做。派現金券畀佢哋買嘢，起碼食飽飯照顧好自己。」<br />\n最近，Magic為匆忙抵英的香港年輕抗爭者提供現金券支援，希望讓他們有基本溫飽，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n對於華南行，對於自己，Magic強調初心沒變，「初。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/biCJl22lnzFEAQFbHgB6U9ToKBA=/510x339/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Y4T7D3S2LND63PNMGI3AGIIAGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbiCJl22lnzFEAQFbHgB6U9ToKBA%3D%2F510x339%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FY4T7D3S2LND63PNMGI3AGIIAGA.jpg&h=2eebe3fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Magic引入Project R產品，包括HONGKONGER衞衣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bqbvhktcJuFIVusXtL08Ya7q-oM=/510x340/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JZIETZV7YBDUHHAF4A2Z23ZKKY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbqbvhktcJuFIVusXtL08Ya7q-oM%3D%2F510x340%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJZIETZV7YBDUHHAF4A2Z23ZKKY.jpg&h=b07d6f6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Magic隨貨附送文宣，盼英國當地多些人留意到香港發生的事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MBBghDqDLRUPhkFboMd2OKXqFQ8=/510x340/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/A4HEEDPYWJAQ7D2ENIZD2HBBCA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMBBghDqDLRUPhkFboMd2OKXqFQ8%3D%2F510x340%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FA4HEEDPYWJAQ7D2ENIZD2HBBCA.jpg&h=6602c2b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■引入的Project R產品包括自由之籽帆布袋及果仁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fvfEY7_WSwDAbD_bihkSItaGMxE=/510x291/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SO27Q2FBLJENLO3PKVBP2RSRDI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfvfEY7_WSwDAbD_bihkSItaGMxE%3D%2F510x291%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSO27Q2FBLJENLO3PKVBP2RSRDI.gif&h=eb6daf76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Magic一直致力引入在港常見而英國罕見的食品，如八角、辣椒醬及港人喜愛口味的薯片。"}]}